---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="YWAM Sendai | Presence. Formation. Mission." isSnap={true}>
  <main>
    
    <section class="h-screen w-full snap-start relative flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-6 text-center">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
        <img src="/hero-sendai.jpg" alt="Sendai Landscape" class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-40 grayscale-[0.2]" />
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-black/10 via-transparent to-dark-bg"></div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="relative z-10">
        <h1 class="text-6xl md:text-9xl font-serif tracking-tighter mb-4">Sendai.</h1>
        <p class="text-gold-accent tracking-[0.4em] uppercase text-xs md:text-sm font-light">Presence • Formation • Mission</p>
      </div>
      <div class="absolute bottom-10 animate-bounce opacity-30 text-[10px] tracking-[0.5em]">SCROLL</div>
    </section>

    <section class="min-h-screen w-full snap-start bg-dark-bg p-8 flex flex-col justify-center">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <span class="text-gold-accent text-xs uppercase tracking-widest block mb-6 text-center">Who We Are</span>
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-serif text-center mb-12">Deep Roots in Tohoku.</h2>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
          <div class="space-y-6 text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed text-lg">
            <p>
              Since 2010, we have been a permanent presence in the heart of Sendai. We are a "Living Monastery"—a YWAM community committed to the <span class="text-zinc-100">One, Holy, Catholic, and Apostolic Church</span>.
            </p>
            <p>
              We bridge Anglican, Orthodox, and Charismatic traditions to create a unified witness in Japan. Our mission is built on <span class="italic text-gold-accent">Theosis</span>—becoming like Christ through His presence.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800 p-8 rounded-[2.5rem]">
            <h3 class="text-zinc-100 font-bold mb-4">Our Commitment</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-4 text-sm">
              <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-gold-accent">†</span> Church Unity in Japan</li>
              <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-gold-accent">†</span> Sustainable Long-term Mission</li>
              <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-gold-accent">†</span> Relational Evangelism</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="min-h-screen w-full snap-start bg-zinc-950 p-6 flex flex-col justify-center">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto w-full">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif mb-10 text-center">Training for the Harvest</h2>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="group relative overflow-hidden bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-800 p-10 rounded-[3rem] hover:border-gold-accent/50 transition-all">
            <h3 class="text-gold-accent text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">Discipleship Training School</h3>
            <h4 class="text-4xl font-serif mb-4 italic">DTS</h4>
            <p class="text-zinc-400 mb-8">A 5-month journey to know God and make Him known. Experience radical transformation in the Tohoku context.</p>
            <div class="flex justify-between items-end border-t border-zinc-800 pt-6">
              <span class="text-xs text-zinc-500 uppercase tracking-widest">Next Start: Sept 2026</span>
              <a href="/en/dts" class="text-xs font-bold underline underline-offset-8">LEARN MORE</a>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="group relative overflow-hidden bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-800 p-10 rounded-[3rem] hover:border-gold-accent/50 transition-all">
            <h3 class="text-gold-accent text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">Discipleship Bible School</h3>
            <h4 class="text-4xl font-serif mb-4 italic">DBS</h4>
            <p class="text-zinc-400 mb-8">12 weeks. The whole Narrative. Find your place in God's story through an inductive study of the Word.</p>
            <div class="flex justify-between items-end border-t border-zinc-800 pt-6">
              <span class="text-xs text-zinc-500 uppercase tracking-widest">Next Start: April 2026</span>
              <a href="/en/dbs" class="text-xs font-bold underline underline-offset-8">LEARN MORE</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="min-h-screen w-full snap-start bg-dark-bg p-8 flex flex-col justify-center">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-serif mb-16 text-center italic text-zinc-400">Our Rhythms in Tohoku</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-12">
          
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="h-px w-12 bg-gold-accent mb-6"></div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold tracking-widest uppercase">Formation</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-zinc-500 leading-relaxed">Through our University of the Nations schools, we provide a sacred space for deep spiritual formation and biblical literacy.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="h-px w-12 bg-gold-accent mb-6"></div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold tracking-widest uppercase">Presence</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-zinc-500 leading-relaxed">Evangelism in Sendai is a ministry of presence. We participate in the life of God as we serve our neighbors in the city.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="h-px w-12 bg-gold-accent mb-6"></div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold tracking-widest uppercase">Compassion</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-zinc-500 leading-relaxed">Mercy is our mandate. We respond to the felt needs of the Tohoku region with the tangible love of Christ.</p>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="h-screen w-full snap-start flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-6 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-serif mb-6 text-white">Begin the Journey.</h2>
      <p class="text-zinc-500 mb-12 max-w-sm text-sm font-sans">
        Whether you have a quick question or feel a pull toward Sendai, we'd love to hear your story.
      </p>
      
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 w-full max-w-xs font-sans">
        <button class="open-hub-trigger w-full py-5 bg-gold-accent text-black font-black rounded-full hover:scale-105 transition-transform uppercase tracking-widest text-xs cursor-pointer">
          Connect
        </button>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
</Layout>